targets.rawSQL:
SELECT DATE_TRUNC('day', activated_at AT TIME ZONE 'America/New_York') AS Date, SKU, SUM(Units) Units
FROM (
    SELECT activated_at
      , CASE p.SKU WHEN 'EMED-195102' THEN '2 Pack' WHEN 'EMED-195201' THEN '6 Pack' ELSE '6 Pack' END as SKU
      , oi.Quantity * p.testkit_quantity AS Units
    FROM default.emed_order_silver o
        INNER JOIN order_salesforce.emed_orderitems oi
            ON o.id = oi.orderid
        INNER JOIN order_salesforce.emed_products p
            ON oi.productid = p.id
    WHERE o.ecomm = 'eComm2'
        AND lower(o.status) IN ('to be fulfilled', 'awaiting shipment', 'shipped', 'created')
        AND oi.type = 'Order Product'
        AND p.sku != 'SHIP'
        AND p.testkit_quantity IN (2, 6)
        AND o.activated_at $__timeFilter
    UNION ALL
    SELECT created_at
      , '6 Pack' AS SKU
      , 6 AS Units
    FROM default.emed_order o
    WHERE lower(o.payment) != 'unpaid'
        AND o.canceled_at is null
        AND o.replace_of IS NULL
        AND o.b2bcode is null
        AND o.created_at $__timeFilter
)
GROUP BY 1, 2
ORDER BY 1

panels.description:
Total Sessions Started - Total number of sessions users initiated (i.e. entered the queue)

Patient and Proctor Connected - Patient and Proctor joined into a session together

Customers in Queue - Current number of customers waiting in queue for a session

User Left Queue - User left before the proctor picked up

Active Sessions - Sessions in progress where an ECG is proctoring a patient

Completed With Result - Total sessions that ended with a positive, negative, inconclusive, or other (could-not-finish) result

Ended Unexpectedly - Total number of sessions that were initiated (a proctor joined) but which ended via an unhappy path (a proctor did not use End Call or submit a result)

Other Drops - Sessions that ended for any other reason

Result (Negative) - Number of Negative test results recorded and reported

Result (Positive) - Number of Positive test results recorded and reported

Result (Invalid) - Number of Invalid test results recorded and reported

Result (Other) - Number of Other test results recorded and reported. These are sessions where a test was consumed, but a result could not be obtained (ex. test dropped on floor, etc.)
